# Ignore non-stowable VS Code assets.
# Variante de keybindings para Linux/Windows: la instala install.sh/install.ps1
# por copia; en macOS no debe enlazarse (allí manda keybindings.json con cmd+).
keybindings\.linux\.json
^/extensions
^/themes
^/scripts
^/package.json
^/CHANGELOG\.md
^/README\.md
^/USAGE\.md
^/Makefile
